item.description:
Here&rsquo;s what I&rsquo;m doing now. Still working at Nintendo, on graphics and tools. This job has been great fun, and I have learned so much about the graphics ecosystem!
Implementing cool 3D Graphics effects in my own engine, written in Jai. Recently&hellip;
Fog Water Skeletal Animation, Inverse Kinematics, etc. Designing a game which feels like Mamoru Oshii&rsquo;s Angel&rsquo;s Egg. This is a small project, and it might start out as a short film.
